OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775718328
OL,3,CProxy bomb driver had gun 'shoved in
OL,4,Cface'
OL,6,FUTV can reveal that the innocent pizza
OL,7,Fdelivery man threatened with death if
OL,8,Fhe didn't bring a bomb to Lurgan
OL,9,Fpolice station had a gun shoved in his
OL,10,Fface just before he drove the crude
OL,11,Fbut deadly device to its target.
OL,13,FMore details of what that terrified
OL,14,Fdriver went through a week ago were
OL,15,Frevealed as police confirmed they are
OL,16,Ftreating the New IRA attack bid as
OL,17,Fattempted murder.
OL,19,FUTV can reveal new details about the
OL,20,Fbomb and the ordeal the driver was put
OL,21,Fthrough on 30 March.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
