PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775718328
OL,3,CProxy bomb driver had gun 'shoved in
OL,4,Cface'
OL,6,FHe was delivering pizzas in the
OL,7,FKilwilkie estate that Monday night
OL,8,Fwhen he was stopped by two masked men
OL,9,F- one had a gun.
OL,11,FUTV can reveal he was ordered out and
OL,12,Ftaken down an alley.
OL,14,FThe gun was then shoved in his face as
OL,15,Fhe was threatened.
OL,17,FIt was then the crude device was put
OL,18,Fin the boot.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775718328
OL,3,CProxy bomb driver had gun 'shoved in
OL,4,Cface'
OL,6,FHe followed those orders to take it to
OL,7,FLurgan police station - but managed to
OL,8,Fraise the alarm.
OL,10,FUTV can also reveal that the device
OL,11,Fwas similar to that used in a terror
OL,12,Fattack at Glasgow Airport in 2007.
OL,14,FThe driver of the vehicle on that
OL,15,Foccasion was one of the attackers - a
OL,16,Fsuicide bomber.
OL,18,FIt was packed with gas cylinders and
OL,19,Fpetrol cans and the driver later died
OL,20,Fof extreme burns.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
