FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775718328
OL,3,CProxy bomb driver had gun 'shoved in
OL,4,Cface'
OL,6,FSenior Security Sources have confirmed
OL,7,Fthe device in Lurgan did not contain
OL,8,Fexplosives but was an incendiary-type
OL,9,Fdevice with a timer attached designed
OL,10,Fto cause a fireball.
OL,12,FPSNI Chief Constable John Boutcher
OL,13,Fsaid the incident is "likely to have
OL,14,Fbeen a sad attempt to appear relevant
OL,15,Fahead of planned dissident Republican
OL,16,Fparades over Easter".
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
